  "text": "The issue of how the presence of multiple risks modify individual behaviour in the face of another risk has been leading to a proli…c literature during the last decades. 1 Most of these studies use monetary measures to analyze behaviour towards risk, the most well-known being the Arrow-Pratt risk premium 2 and the willingness to pay [CITATION_1] .",
